  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've just been hired at SmashFest: A combat sports company with a violent corporate culture. Fight your way up the corporate ladder and find what it means to be a white collar champion.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Destroy Everything</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990680/extras/3faf1aeb96797ac854b2a8fbd3764a02.poster.avif?t=1762540031\" width=604 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990680/extras/3faf1aeb96797ac854b2a8fbd3764a02.webm?t=1762540031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990680/extras/3faf1aeb96797ac854b2a8fbd3764a02.mp4?t=1762540031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nothing is nailed down and everything can be bashed to bits.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Destroy Everyone</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990680/extras/4f6aae9514e61b18e1cf7160c95e3064.poster.avif?t=1762540031\" width=500 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990680/extras/4f6aae9514e61b18e1cf7160c95e3064.webm?t=1762540031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990680/extras/4f6aae9514e61b18e1cf7160c95e3064.mp4?t=1762540031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leave no coworker left standing... by any means necessary.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Smash in your own style</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990680/extras/7942f639927a11bfdb6d0e37817b598b.poster.avif?t=1762540031\" width=604 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990680/extras/7942f639927a11bfdb6d0e37817b598b.webm?t=1762540031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990680/extras/7942f639927a11bfdb6d0e37817b598b.mp4?t=1762540031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn new moves from the legends of SmashFest and make your own perfect combination! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...or just go full haymakers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock Questionable Promotions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rising up in this company means getting REAL upgrades. From better vending machines, to full on insurance fraud... take advantage of every opportunity.  </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've just been hired at SmashFest: A combat sports company with a violent corporate culture. Fight your way up the corporate ladder and find what it means to be a white collar champion.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Destroy Everything</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990680/extras/3faf1aeb96797ac854b2a8fbd3764a02.poster.avif?t=1762540031\" width=604 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990680/extras/3faf1aeb96797ac854b2a8fbd3764a02.webm?t=1762540031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990680/extras/3faf1aeb96797ac854b2a8fbd3764a02.mp4?t=1762540031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nothing is nailed down and everything can be bashed to bits.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Destroy Everyone</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990680/extras/4f6aae9514e61b18e1cf7160c95e3064.poster.avif?t=1762540031\" width=500 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990680/extras/4f6aae9514e61b18e1cf7160c95e3064.webm?t=1762540031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990680/extras/4f6aae9514e61b18e1cf7160c95e3064.mp4?t=1762540031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leave no coworker left standing... by any means necessary.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Smash in your own style</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990680/extras/7942f639927a11bfdb6d0e37817b598b.poster.avif?t=1762540031\" width=604 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990680/extras/7942f639927a11bfdb6d0e37817b598b.webm?t=1762540031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990680/extras/7942f639927a11bfdb6d0e37817b598b.mp4?t=1762540031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn new moves from the legends of SmashFest and make your own perfect combination! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...or just go full haymakers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock Questionable Promotions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rising up in this company means getting REAL upgrades. From better vending machines, to full on insurance fraud... take advantage of every opportunity.  </p>",
